# News & Media Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 📰 NEWS REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define content categories
   - [ ] Plan content hierarchy
   - [ ] Identify user roles
   - [ ] List required features
   - [ ] Document editorial workflow

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] AMP compatibility

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Breaking news alerts
   - [ ] Live updates
   - [ ] Category navigation
   - [ ] Search functionality
   - [ ] Subscription system
   - [ ] Comments system
   - [ ] Social sharing
   - [ ] Push notifications

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── news/
│   │   ├── ArticleCard.tsx
│   │   ├── ArticleGrid.tsx
│   │   ├── ArticleDetail.tsx
│   │   └── LiveUpdates.tsx
│   ├── media/
│   │   ├── VideoPlayer.tsx
│   │   ├── Gallery.tsx
│   │   └── AudioPlayer.tsx
│   ├── subscription/
│   │   ├── PaywallModal.tsx
│   │   └── SubscriptionPlans.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx
│       ├── BreakingNews.tsx
│       └── ShareButtons.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── news/
│   ├── categories/
│   ├── live/
│   └── search/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Content Structure
1. **Article Format**
   - Headlines: 60-70 characters
   - Subheadlines: 120-140 characters
   - Featured image: 1200x630px
   - Body: Rich text with multimedia
   - Related articles

2. **Typography**
   - Headlines: 28-32px
   - Body text: 18-20px
   - Line height: 1.6
   - Font: Clear, readable sans-serif

3. **Layout Principles**
   - Article width: 680px-720px
   - Sidebar width: 300px-320px
   - Ad spaces: IAB standards
   - Breaking news banner

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Content Loading**
   - Initial page load < 2s
   - Lazy loading images
   - Content preloading
   - AMP compatibility

2. **Real-time Updates**
   - WebSocket connection
   - Push notifications
   - Live content updates
   - Breaking news alerts

3. **Media Handling**
   - Adaptive streaming
   - Image optimization
   - Video compression
   - Audio optimization

## 🔒 Editorial System

1. **Content Management**
   - Editorial workflow
   - Version control
   - Scheduled publishing
   - Content moderation

2. **User Management**
   - Role-based access
   - Editor dashboard
   - Content approval
   - Analytics access

